    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the hood, and a few minor dings from parking lots. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant bolster wear, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to bring it back to peak performance. It is a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and age.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
